                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4509" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0644</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9067 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东阿阿胶业绩爆雷，是意外还是必然？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ejiao had a poor performance in 2019, was it an accident or inevitable event?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧，郁静怡，陆叶，廖昌</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东阿阿胶</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东阿阿胶；应收账款；坏账准备；存货跌价准备；迁徙率模型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ejiao; Accounts receivable; Provision for bad debts; Provision for inventory depreciation; Migration rate model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年1月19日，东阿阿胶发布关于2019年年度业绩预告的公告。公司预计，归属于上市公司股东的净利润为亏损3.336亿元至4.586亿元，比上年同期下降116%至122%，去年同期为盈利20.85亿元。据WIND数据，这是公司自1993以来首次出现亏损，即27年首亏。作为中国医药行业的龙头之一，东阿阿胶的净利润连续十二年保持着增长的态势，成为了市场公认的“白马股”。27年不遇的亏损就这样猝不及防地降临了，让坚守“白马股”的投资者都有些措手不及。业绩的突然爆雷，是意外还是必然？“药中茅台”是在“洗大澡”还是业绩真的凉凉了？本案例拟从财务报表分析的视角，尤其是从应收账款的迁徙率模型和准备矩阵的维度，引导学生掌握如何对识别企业财务报表粉饰的动机和风险，尤其是应收账款和存货两个重要资产项目的粉饰风险及预警信号，进而提升学生对公司整体财务报表的分析与判断能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On January 19, 2020, Ejiao issued an announcement on the forecast of its 2019 finance performance. The company expected that the net profit attributable to shareholders would be a loss between 333.6 million yuan and 458.6 million yuan, which was a decrease of 116% to 122% over last year. According to WIND data, this was the company&#39;s first loss since 1993, meaning besides 2019 Ejiao had not had loss for 27 years. As one of the leaders in China&#39;s pharmaceutical industry, Ejiao&#39;s net profit has maintained a growth trend for twelve years so that it has become a recognized &quot;white horse stock&quot; in the market. The investors who believed in Ejiao were caught off guard because of this first loss on net profit after 27-year successful operating. Is this sudden explosion of performance accidental or inevitable? Does &quot; Medicine’s Moutai &quot; really go down? This case intends to guide students from the perspective of financial statement analysis, especially from the migration rate model of the accounts receivable and the preparation matrix model, to understand the motivations and risks of making up corporate financial statements, especially on the   accounts receivable and inventory. The risks and early warning signals of these two important assets will further enhance students&#39; ability to analyze and judge the company&#39;s overall financial statements. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计》、《财务报表分析》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务报表分析、应收账款坏账准备计提、存货跌价准备计提合理性分析</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-06</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
